      "time": "~20s",
      "narrative": "- Once the agents are running, the next question is simple.\n- Are they doing the job the right way?\n- This section stays close to the invoice-review task and shows how we inspect quality in Foundry.",
      "demo_actions": "Open the Foundry post-deployment view and frame this chapter as performance inspection.",
