        "design_plan": false
      },
      "time": "~30s",
      "narrative": "- Once the rubric is defined, run evaluations against it.\n- Now we can see where the agent is strong and where it still needs work.\n- This is much better than relying on anecdotal testing or one-off examples.",
      "demo_actions": "Run or review evaluation results. Show scores, failures, and examples.",
